Tags:
  - 902
By: Ibn 'Arabi
---
When the (metallic) substance attains the form of gold, it departs from
the hold of the physician (artist), since it departs from its state of
sickness. Once perfection has been attained, a relapse into imperfection is
henceforth out of the question, even should the physician try to provoke it.
